# Livo Phase 0 — Foundation Complete

## What Was Built

**Expo SDK 52 + TypeScript project** scaffolded and verified clean at `npx tsc --noEmit` with `strict: true` and `noImplicitAny: true`.

---

## Key Decision: `@types` path alias

TypeScript reserves the `@types/*` module specifier for DefinitelyTyped packages, so the alias was renamed to `@app-types/*` in both [tsconfig.json](file:///Users/vatsalchaturvedi/Livo_FrontEnd/tsconfig.json) and [babel.config.js](file:///Users/vatsalchaturvedi/Livo_FrontEnd/babel.config.js). Every file that imports from the types folder uses `@app-types/...`.

