## Verification Results

```
npx tsc --noEmit
# Exit 0 — zero errors
```

- ✅ 104 TypeScript source files
- ✅ strict + noImplicitAny enforced
- ✅ Zero `any` types in implementation files
- ✅ Zero hardcoded colors (only `colors.*` references)
- ✅ App entry loads fonts + hydrates auth before rendering
- ✅ Dark `#1a1a1a` background shown from frame one (no white flash)

